Package com.fortify.client.fod.api.query.builder

This package provides various builder classes used to configure REST queries and building a corresponding FoDEntityQuery instance.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AbstractFoDEntityQueryBuilder.IFoDEntityQueryBuilderParamFields<T extends AbstractFoDEntityQueryBuilder<T>>
    This interface is to be implemented by all AbstractFoDEntityQueryBuilder implementations that expose the various paramFields*() methods.
    AbstractFoDEntityQueryBuilder.IFoDEntityQueryBuilderParamFilter<T extends AbstractFoDEntityQueryBuilder<T>>
    This interface is to be implemented by all AbstractFoDEntityQueryBuilder implementations that expose the various paramFilter*() methods.
    AbstractFoDEntityQueryBuilder.IFoDEntityQueryBuilderParamOrderByWithDirection<T extends AbstractFoDEntityQueryBuilder<T>>
    This interface is to be implemented by all AbstractFoDEntityQueryBuilder implementations that expose the AbstractFoDEntityQueryBuilder.IFoDEntityQueryBuilderParamOrderByWithDirection.paramOrderBy(IfBlankAction, FoDOrderBy) method.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractFoDApplicationChildEntityQueryBuilder<T extends AbstractFoDApplicationChildEntityQueryBuilder<T>>
    This abstract base class is used to build FoDEntityQuery instances for querying FoD application child entities.
    AbstractFoDEntityQueryBuilder<T extends AbstractFoDEntityQueryBuilder<T>>
    This abstract base class is used to build FoDEntityQuery instances.
    AbstractFoDReleaseChildEntityQueryBuilder<T extends AbstractFoDReleaseChildEntityQueryBuilder<T>>
    This abstract base class is used to build FoDEntityQuery instances for querying FoD release child entities.
    FoDApplicationsQueryBuilder
    This class allows for building an FoDEntityQuery instance that allows for querying FoD applications.
    FoDOrderBy  
    FoDReleasesQueryBuilder
    This class allows for building an FoDEntityQuery instance that allows for querying FoD releases.
    FoDReleaseVulnerabilitiesQueryBuilder
    This class allows for building an FoDEntityQuery instance that allows for querying FoD release vulnerabilities.
    FoDReleaseVulnerabilityFiltersQueryBuilder
    This class allows for building an FoDEntityQuery instance that allows for querying FoD release vulnerability filters.
    FoDScansQueryBuilder
    This class allows for building an FoDEntityQuery instance that allows for querying FoD applications.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FoDOrderByDirection
    This enumeration allows for specifying whether REST query results should be ordered in ascending or descending order.

Package com.fortify.client.fod.api.query.builder Description

This package provides various builder classes used to configure REST queries and building a corresponding FoDEntityQuery instance.
